<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Stars found ways to honor their daughters for National Daughter's Day on Friday. </p>

<p>And Angelina Jolie treated her girls Zahara and Vivienne to dinner at celebrity hotspot Craigs in West Hollywood. </p>

<p>The Salt actress kept her look simple for the girls' night out, opting for a black sheath dress. </p>

<p>Girls night: Angelina Jolie treated her girls Zahara and Vivienne to dinner at celebrity hotspot Craigs in West Hollywood, on National Daughter's Day, Friday</p>

<p>The 45-year-old actress opted for a dress with long-sleeves, a high boat-neck, and an empire waist. </p>

<p>Keeping her look simple, she carried a back and gold Valentino crossbody bag on her shoulder. </p>

<p>She left her dark brown hair in a sleek and straight style, parted in the middle, as she covered her face in a blue medical face mask. </p>

<p>Zahara, 15, whom Angelina adopted in 2005 at six-months-old, led her mother and sister on their way into the restaurant. </p>

<p>Casual: They all cut casual looks as Zahara, 15, led her mom and sister inside</p>

<p>She looked stylish and casual, opting for high-waisted medium wash denim jeans with distressed tears at her knees. </p>

<p>Keeping cool, she paired the pants with a black tube top, matching face mask and white sneakers. </p>

<p>Meanwhile Vivienne, 12, chose a beige sweatshirt, light wash jeans and matched her mom in a blue face mask. </p>

<p>It was a girls only night, as the actress left her four other children—Maddox, 19, Pax, 16, John, 14, and Vivienne's twin brother Knox, 12— whom she shares with ex Brad Pitt, at home. </p>

<p>All together now: It was a girls only night, as the actress left her four other children—Maddox, 19, Pax, 16, John, 14, and Vivienne's twin brother Knox, 12— who she shares with ex Brad Pitt, at home </p>

<p>This comes after the One And Only Ivan actress told E!'s Daily Pop that she loves the 'chaos' of it all with dogs running around, balls being thrown and movie nights with heaps of popcorn in her $25M Los Feliz mansion.</p>

<p>'You know, I've never been one who valued relaxation. I like chaos,' the former model said with a laugh.</p>

<p>'I've been on high-level meetings where there's dogs and balls and kids and things. You kind of just enjoy being human with everybody else and laughing through it.</p>

<p>Her outing and comments come amid ongoing legal battles in her divorce from Brad.</p>

<p>Trouble: Earlier this month, reports said relations between the former couple who share six children have deteriorated to the point where they are no longer engaging in family therapy ahead of a custody trial slated for next month, UsWeekly reported Thursday (pictured in 2005) </p>

<p>Earlier this month, reports said relations between the former couple who share six children have deteriorated to the point where they are no longer engaging in family therapy ahead of a custody trial slated for next month, UsWeekly reported Thursday.  </p>

<p>'Brad wants 50/50 joint physical and legal custody of the kids. Angelina has been unagreeable to those terms,' a source told UsWeekly.</p>

<p>The insider added that Jolie 'will only agree to talk about an agreement if the home base for the children isn't Los Angeles. The younger kids are in school in Los Angeles, which Angelina has always been opposed to.'</p>

<p>It's previously been suggested that Jolie wants to relocate to the UK and base the children with her there. </p>
